cotton.servicediscovery

Class DiscoveryPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • cotton.servicediscovery.DiscoveryPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DiscoveryPacket
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The DiscoveryPacket acts as a wrapper for the DiscoveryProbe and the AnnouncePacket. Each packet consists of a DiscoveryPacketType used to determine the packet purpose.
    See Also:
    DiscoveryProbe, AnnouncePacket, Serialized Form
